column2: "...Waiting, I was. I, we... have been waiting for this moment."
"First I must thank you. Without your co-operation, this moment would not have come."
"Because you were there... Now, in this present, you are here, she is here, I and we are here."
"Now, just add the finishing touches... and it will be the end."
"...The core of the Oracle. I wish for you and Matoi to go to the heart of the Mothership."
"...<%me>. Xion. You two are acting... a little different today."
"Off to the heart?... I wonder what's in store."
